                <h1>Two members of the Exonerated Five to speak at Duke next week</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/53e1da97-3685-4362-b6ca-ddd92b4fad0e.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;Members&#x20;of&#x20;the&#x20;Exonerated&#x20;Five&#x20;with&#x20;Ken&#x20;Burns&#x20;after&#x20;the&#x20;2012&#x20;documentary&#x20;about&#x20;their&#x20;case.&#x20;Raymond&#x20;Santana&#x20;&#x28;left&#x29;&#x20;and&#x20;Yusef&#x20;Salaam&#x20;&#x28;second-from-left&#x29;&#x20;are&#x20;speaking&#x20;at&#x20;Duke&#x20;next&#x20;week.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>Members of the Exonerated Five with Ken Burns after the 2012 documentary about their case. Raymond Santana (left) and Yusef Salaam (second-from-left) are speaking at Duke next week.</p>

                                                            <aside class="photo-caption photo-credit d-inline pl-1">
